# CD and navigating within the project

- Memorize where project root dir is
- Never go outside the project!
- Remember where the project root is
- Do not do `cd ../..` multiple times. This is an issue where you go outside and commands stops working
- NEVER run app separately. ONLY run all apps together! ONLY from root of the project and with `pnpm dev`! Otherwise you will get ports conflict and it will not work...
- YOU DO NOT NEED TO RESTART SERVER SEPARATELY! WHEN YOU RUN `PNPM DEV` FROM THE ROOT, IT KILLS ALL THE PREVIOUS PROCESSES AND RELEASES PORTS.
- Do not modify anything else that was not asked to be modified!
